ention, 1\nsympathy and solicitation.\nAfterwards she had to begin\ngrowing up again.\nPsychiatrists have discovered\nthat post-operative delirium j\nhas been misdiagnosed as a\nmajor psychosis, sometimes, j\nThis type of post-operative be\nhavior should, the authors say,\njbe investigated for possible ln\nsection, drug toxicity and fluid\nimbalance.\nActually, irrational fears and;\nreactions to surgical experi-\nences are frequent.\nI Explanation Helps\nMorbid introspection and ap\nprehension often can be re\nduced. the authors sky. by a\nforthright explanation of the j\nentire process of the operation.\nThe physicians agree that\nspecial consideration should be\ns given to maintaining the pa\ntient\u2019s ties with his family. Cer-\nI tainly, children feel more secure\nwhen given a favorite toy to\nl keep with them.\nA key member of the family\ndefinitely should be present\nafter an operation,\ni Sympathetic and optimistic\nI honesty is vital on the part of\nthe physician before and after\nsurgery, they say. And make\nthe child feel as close to home\nas possible, before and after.\ni Reserves to Meet\nBranch No. 4 of the Fleet\nReserve Association will meet at\ni 8 p.m. tomorrow at\\the Amer\nican Legion clubhouse, 433\nI Third street N.W. Officers will!\n1 be elected.\nADVERTISEMENT\nBackache\nNEW YORK Special: Thanks to new,\nsclentiflc laboratory formulation, thou-\nI sands of men and women now escape\nfeelint old. tired. Irritable and depressed\nfrom losing sleep and worrying about\nI \u201cBladder Weakness\u201d -(Getting Up Nights\nor Bed Wetting!. due to common Kidney\nor Bladder Irritation*, which often re\nsult In secondary Backache. Headache\nand Nervousness. In such cases New\nImproved CYSTEX usually gives quick,\ncalming relief by combating irritating\ngerms In acid urine; and by relaxing,\nanalgesic pain relief. Over a billion\nCYSTEX tablets used\u2014proves safety for\nyoung and old. Get Laboratory Tested\nand Certified CYSTEX at drugalst today.\nS